  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Anorexia nervosa (AN) is a complex and severe psychiatric disorder with high relapse rates
      under standard treatment.Deep brain stimulation (DBS) may be a novel treatment in severe
      Anorexia nervosa.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
